preference.name: CATIA_catalog_comp_dataset_types
preference.preference_description: List of dataset types used when saving certain documents referenced in a catalog. These documents could be CATScripts, CATSystems, Word documents or similar and excludes parts, products, drawings, V4 models, processes, analysis, catalog, foreign files. A specific document is stored in the first dataset type compatible with its type.
